snippet.description:
Toronto-bred duo Torro Torro have released a new video for 'Make A Move.' The song is out on OWSLA along with a pack of new remixes from Skrillex, Habstrakt and Star Slinger x Mark Johns. The video features buzzing skaters Dashawn Jordan, Marcell Herd, Benjamin Cortez, Justin Damer and actress/model Chelsea Debo making her skating debut. It was filmed in the streets of San Francisco and directed by Alexandre Souetre and Ryan Neddeau of Steve Berra’s Berrics crew.
